        <item>
            <title>v1.20.0: Auto-shrink menu bar icon</title>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[
                    <p>v1.20.0</p>
                    <p>Auto-shrink the menu bar icon when there is not enough room.</p>
                    <p>When the menu bar icon is too wide to fit, Spaceman progressively shrinks it: first to compact numbers-only, then to the app icon. The icon unshrinks automatically when you switch spaces, trigger a manual refresh, or click the app icon.</p>
                    <p>Note: this option is enabled by default.</p>
                ]]>
